Class CareerCenterStaff

java.lang.Object
src.entity.User
src.entity.CareerCenterStaff
public class CareerCenterStaff extends User
Represents a career center staff member who extends the base `User`.

Career center staff have a department and a role and are typically responsible for administrative actions within the career center scope.
